dot-files
=========
gitified dot-files for *nix boxes. Just clone the files to your box and link appropriately to get an unified experience. 


To clone the files to your box:

cd ~
git clone git@github.com:khalavak/dot-files.git ~/.dotfiles

cd ~/.dotfiles
git submodule init
git submodule update
ln -s ~/.dotfiles/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/.dotfiles/.vim ~/.vim
ln -s ~/.dotfiles/.bashrc ~/.bashrc
ln -s ~/.dotfiles/.conkyrc ~/.conkyrc                                            


To update all git modules :

git submodule foreach git pull branch master

